{"word":"G3076 - λυπέω - lypéō - loo-peh'-o - Cause grief","slug":"G3076","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">λυπέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>lypéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>loo-peh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Cause grief"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BB;&#x03C5;&#x03C0;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - lupeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>loo-peh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G3077\">G3077</a>; to <i>distress</i>; reflexively or passively to <i>be sad:</i> - cause grief, grieve, be in heaviness, (be) sorrow (-ful), be (make) sorry."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G253\">G253</a>, <a href=\"#/G3077\">G3077</a>, <a href=\"#/G4036\">G4036</a>, <a href=\"#/G4818\">G4818</a>"}]}